title: Checkmk: Site Broker Status
agents: linux
catalog: app/cmk
license: GPLv2
distribution: check_mk
description:
 This check monitors the general status of the message broker for each site.

 The service shows the memory used by the broker, the number of queues,
 and the number of shovels in _running_ state.
 The check status is always {OK}.

item:
 The name of the site.

discovery:
 One service is create for each site where the broker is installed and running.
